Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.77,0:19:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們鶴賀估計要陷入苦戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心  並不是放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.81,0:19:58.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果前半能咬住比分進入後半的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:04.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的勝負  就看副將戰和大將戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:25.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天…決勝負！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡笑還是淚水都在明天了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.83,0:20:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就是決賽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.36,0:20:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了就能進全國大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.58,0:20:44.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸了就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.80,0:21:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:34.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原村同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.17,0:21:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早  原村同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.12,0:21:43.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.71,0:21:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.81,0:21:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.01,0:21:52.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家到齊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.21,0:21:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
